(The alternate YOLO detector may be retrained using darkflow as suggested).

body:
The default detector in the demo now uses SSD Mobilenet, which can be retrained with the [TF Object Detection API](https://github.com/tensorflow/models/tree/master/object_detection).

(The alternate YOLO detector may be retrained using darkflow as suggested).
